%h3 Students

- @company.company_feeds.showable.each do |feed|
	.student
		= link_to feed.student.name, feed.student
		(score: #{feed.score})
		= link_to "star", star_student_path(feed.student)
		| 
		= link_to "dismiss", dismiss_student_path(feed.student)
		%br



